      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 84,
      "message": "Maybe a little bit less fancy but more readable:\n\n```\nprivate fun <T> overwriteFields(base: Option<T>, update: Option<T>, overrider: (base: T, update: T) -> T) =\n        when {\n            base is Some && update is Some -> overrider(base.t, update.t).toOption()\n            base is Some && update is None -> base\n            base is None && update is Some -> update\n            else -> None\n        }\n```\n\nWhich by the way can be renamed to something more general (don't have any idea of the name) and moved to org.onap.dcae.collectors.veshv.utils.arrow/core.kt.",
